      <h3>
        <p>
          <i>SciNote</i> is a top-rated platform for researchers in federal, state, or local governments as
          well as academia or industry, who need electronic laboratory and/or field notebook, inventory
          management and project management functionalities. SciNote organizes your data by projects,
          experiments and tasks, which gives structure and context to all your experimental data. Use your
          notes, excel sheets, tables, checklists or pictures to create print-ready protocols and kick-start
          your lab or field work. When you are done, upload your results. In SciNote all your data is
          searchable, accessible and traceable. SciNote runs on an EPA private cloud installation via EPA RTP
          RedHat Enterprise VM and has the following features currently available: 2 TB+ of storage, Unlimited
